      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Why we need API?\n\n- Application Programming Interface\n\n- Works as a messenger to exachange information between two application.\n\n    1. Speed and Reusable\n    2. Seamless Integration\n    3. Security\n    4. Scalable",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
