      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FAST API for Agentic AI?\n\n- Async -> Perfect for LLM to compelte it in a sec\n- Streaming-> native SSE support for LLm tokens to send to frontend\n- Pydantic -> data validation\n- Automatic documentation\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
